      <p>
	Allows the user to make a weapon flame for the
	duration of a combat. Flaming weapons do +d6 extra
	fire damage.  The flame is magical and will not burn
	wooden weapons.
      </p>

      <p>
	In the event of overcharge the caster suffers 2d6 fire
	damage.
      </p>
